<h1>Quiz finished</h1>
Congratulations. You completed the quiz.<br />
Due to security reasons I removed email sending from the application. Just left the stat on the finish page. You are free to send it yourself. 
<table class="table">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th>Question</th>
			<th>Result</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<% @answers.each do |answer| %>
			<tr>
				<td><%= answer[:id] %></td>
				<td><%= answer[:correct] %></td>
			</tr>
		<% end %>
	</tbody>
</table> 
